snippet.title: Autodesk Fusion 360
snippet.description:
Autodesk’s Fusion 360 is the 3D CAD/CAM/CAE/PCB and cloud collaboration software mechanical engineers, industrial designers and machinists use to design, engineer, simulate, and manufacture their products. 
This channel is all about teaching you actionable tips on how to use Fusion 360’s fully integrated multi-disciplinary workspaces, intuitive workflows, and powerful features to grow your business. 
Tune in to our podcast, “The New Possible,” where we shed light on the future of making things. Each episode tells the story of how a company unlocked their new possible using Fusion 360.
